title: Luis Carlos planning an email reminded me of an emperor planning a speech.
pid: 4a6933e2-0026-431a-b0d8-5ee9d780336a
body: |2-
  <2024-01-11 Thu>

  He held a meeting with a few advisors in which we discussed how to phrase good news to employees and importers. Had to not overpromise, but also make it unlikely that the unions or the importers would complain.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
